<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/wilton-park> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Wilton Park is the UK government’s expert in convening international policy dialogue. It supports UK foreign policy development and the UK government’s international strategic priorities. Wilton Park holds around 80 strategic dialogues each year, which convene around 3,500 representatives and opinion formers, representing over 120 countries. Wilton Park is an executive agency, sponsored by the Foreign, Commonwealth & Development Office ."@en <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/rdfa> .
